      "writtenOn": "2023-10-04T12:58:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "repo:voltha-docs contains a makefile target linkcheck (ie: make test) that will sanity check document URLs.  \n\nIntermittent failures have been reported at times while trying to resolve/verify each url.  Unfortunately these have also manifested in jenkins.\n\nhttps will add a mild bit of overhead by adding encryption.\n\nFor URLs that do not require a secure connection, using simple http VS https out of the box helps reduce webserver load.\n\nFor document checking, it will also help shrink potential for intermittent linkcheck failure points.",
